                        | I'm a technology enthusiast, master in computer science, currently working as full stack developer. My research area in graduate and postgraduate was mainly augmented reality, virtual reality, computer graphics and informatics for education.  I'm interested in web systems, software development and software architecture.
                    .social-icons
                        a.social-icon(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/lidiane-t-pereira')
                            i.fab.fa-linkedin-in
                        a.social-icon(href='https://github.com/lidianetpereira')
                            i.fab.fa-github
                        a.social-icon(href='https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Lidiane-Pereira-3')
