            hr.m-0

            // Experience
            section#experience.resume-section
               .resume-section-content
                    h2.mb-5 Experience

                    .d-flex.flex-column.flex-md-row.justify-content-between.mb-5
                        .flex-grow-1
                            h3.mb-0 Full stack developer
                            .subheading.mb-3 Banib
                            p
                                | I work on development and maintenance of a SaaS for virtual tours creation.  I am involved in the entire software improvement and evolution cycle, contributing in requirements analysis, modeling and implementation. As a full stack, I work both on the backend (developed in Spring Boot and Java, with PostgreSQL relational database) creating REST APIs, and on the frontend (developed in Vue.js with Typescript). 
                        .flex-shrink-0
                            span.text-primary September 2021 - Present

            hr.m-0

            // Education
            section#education.resume-section
                .resume-section-content
                    h2.mb-5 Education

                    .d-flex.flex-column.flex-md-row.justify-content-between.mb-5
                        .flex-grow-1
                            h3.mb-0 Universidade Federal de Juiz de Fora
                            .subheading.mb-3 Master in Computer Science
                            p
                                | My research aimed to use photo realism in Augmented Reality applications. To achieve this, we proposed ARRay - Tracing, a framework for using ray tracing in AR applications through the combined use of OptiX, VKRay and ARToolKit.
                        .flex-shrink-0
                            span.text-primary 2019 - 2021

                    .d-flex.flex-column.flex-md-row.justify-content-between
                        .flex-grow-1
                            h3.mb-0 Universidade Federal de Juiz de Fora
